snippet.title: Labyrinths of the World: Secrets of Easter Island
snippet.description: Domini Games presents the newest addition to the Labyrinths of the World series! MI6 has rewarded you with a vacation to thank you for saving the world. What starts as a relaxing getaway quickly takes a disastrous turn as your world is attacked by an ancient god and their stone statues! Can you stop the destruction before it's too late? Find out in this rousing Hidden-Object Puzzle adventure!
